732933f.title: Social conditions in Manhattan.
732933f.text:
Sdcial Conditions in Manhattan: This picture shows the community
sink from which eighteen people draw all their water on the top floor
of No. 72 Greenwich Street. The toilets for the four-story house adjoin
the sink. Published in the New York Evening World of February 23, 1926.
February 23, 1926.
Gift of New York world.
